	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S. D.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Rursus, mi frater <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p1789" cert="high">Kesslere</persName>, lugubres ad te literas scribo domino deo nostro sic res nostras temperante pro sancta bonaque sua voluntate.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Mortuus est hac nocte praeterita ad horam 11. clarissimus et san[c]tissimus vir d. <persName ref="p1283" cert="high">Conradus Gessnerus</persName>, singulare totius Helvetiae, nedum Tigurinorum decus.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Occuparat praecordia eius anthrax pestilentissimus, et bubo insederat sub axilla eius sinistra.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Dominica praeterita fuit adhuc in coetu sacro, prout erat diligentissimus concionum mearum auditor.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Salutabat me pro more.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Mox aegrotare coepit, nunquam tamen decubuit; cum enim paululum se in lectum composuisset, mox iterum consurgens obambulabat aut considebat.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Semper de rebus san[c]tis et utilibus disserebat, quinimo in extremum usque spiritu laborabat, homo alioqui exhaustus laboribus.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Heri multa ipse adhuc scripsit, apprehensa vero dextera mea mihi valedixit etc. fidem suam professus et certissimam spem vitae aeternae per Iesum Christum etc.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vides dominum deum nostrum doctissimos quosque optimosque viros evocare ex hoc mundo.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quid futurum sit, ipse pro tua pietate iudicas.</s>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Valde te oro, mi domine et frater, ut hunc literarum fasciculum <placeName ref="l1976" cert="high">Augustam</placeName> mitti cures per <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p1918">Linerum</persName> nostrum vel per amicos nostros tuto et, quam potest fieri, cito.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Scribo amico meo <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p3740">Georgio a Stetten</persName>; is curabit literas meas inscriptas secretario et medico imperatoris, singularibus amicis meis.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Scribo haec in magno meo moerore.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ora pro nobis.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Saluta filium tuum, ministros omnes, charissimos fratres, <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p1918">Linerum</persName> et alios.</s>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vale.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="18" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tiguri 14. decembris 1565.</s>
					<s n="19" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Sub vesperam efferetur ad horam 4.</s>
					<s n="20" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName type="citizen_name" ref="p495" cert="high">Bullingerus</persName> tuus.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="21" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ornatissimo viro d. <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p1789" cert="high">Ioanni Kesslero</persName> <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l474" cert="high">Sangallensi</placeName>, domino meo colendo et fratri charissimo.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="22" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Dem herren schuͦlmeister <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p1789" cert="high">Kesslern</persName> zuͦ <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l474" cert="high">Santgallen</placeName>.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
